  <summary>10/7/2004--Introduced.
American Indian Veterans Pay Restoration Act of 2004 - Directs the Secretary concerned to pay to each person who is a qualifying Indian veteran an amount equal to the amount of that person's basic pay withheld as State income tax for periods of time during which that person was in active service and domiciled in Indian country.</summary>
